title: DDFP 378: NFC West preview
itunes:title: DDFP 378: NFC West preview
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank to break down the latest storylines surrounding the NFC West. The guys also review J.J Watt's showing during the first episode of "Hard Knocks." Shek then wraps up the show by bringing in Ross Tucker of "The Ross Tucker Football Podcast" to talk training camp stories and the prospects of a NFL team returning to Los Angeles.
